{"word":"ἀνωφελής","slug":"ἀνωφελής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνωφελής</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὠφελέω'><el>ὠφελέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>unprofitable, useless</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>hurtful, prejudicial</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> to one, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-λῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}